# =================================================================
# ðŸ“‹ SETUP CHECKLIST
# =================================================================
# For a basic working GSA Leasing MVP, you need:
#
# âœ… MUST HAVE (App breaks without these):
#    1. DATABASE_URL (from Neon)
#    2. NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL (from Supabase)
#    3. NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY (from Supabase)
#    4. SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY (from Supabase)
#    5. SAM_API_KEY (from SAM.gov)
#    6. NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY (from Google Cloud)
#    7. NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL (your domain/localhost)
